node.text:
From being undrafted to being cut 3x before being sent to NFL Europe & being cut again after I got back, I smiled thru it all. None of it changed how felt about myself & my skills. It just fueled me to prove ALL of them wrong.🔥🔥🔥 What fuels you?

#DeeboFuel 🔥 #findyourfuel #findyourmotivation #motivation #MotivatedByDeebo #Deebo #DeeboGear
